(1683, 1, '2011-08-10 14:47:19', '2011-08-10 20:47:19', '<a href="http://the10centdesigner.com/blog/2011/08/10/making-wind/canned-air/" rel="attachment wp-att-1684"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-1684" title="canned air" src="http://the10centdesigner.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/canned-air-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></a>\n\nFunny story. Getty Images requested <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/theproletariatdesigner/5799757865/in/set-72157600885932418" target="_blank">one of my fav instagram image''s</a> for licensing. <a href="http://the10centdesigner.com/blog/2011/08/10/making-wind/original-image/" rel="attachment wp-att-1686"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-1686" title="original image" src="http://the10centdesigner.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/original-image-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></a>(Second image on this page)\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWell, I shot it directly in instagram so obviously the file size is far too small for them to actually accept. So I thought I would try to recreate it. Not as simple as I hoped. The day I actually shot it the skies were slightly overcast and there was a nice big breeze. I just couldn''t get the dress to move the same way. Until Buckarooken brought out the big guns. <a href="http://the10centdesigner.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/canned-air.jpg" target="_blank">Literally</a>. He has a massive air compressor in the garage, We used it and set up our own wind. Funny. The neighbors surely enjoyed the sight while they ate their dinner next door. Hopefully my new version will still make it into the Getty flickr collection, if not, we had a "blast" shooting it. get it? blast. teehee\n\n<a href="http://the10centdesigner.com/blog/2011/08/10/making-wind/the-recreation/" rel="attachment wp-att-1685"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-1685" title="the recreation" src="http://the10centdesigner.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/the-recreation-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></a>', 'making wind', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'making-wind', '', '', '2011-08-10 14:47:19', '2011-08-10 20:47:19', '', 0, 'http://the10centdesigner.com/blog/?p=1683', 0, 'post', '', 0),
