(1970, 1, '2012-03-19 13:19:29', '2012-03-19 19:19:29', 'The results of <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/theproletariatdesigner/sets/72157629256707512/">my</a> artistic collaboration with <a href="http://shaneyuhas.com/">Shane Yuhas</a> are FINALLY starting to get posted to flickr.\n\n[flickr size="large"]http://www.flickr.com/photos/theproletariatdesigner/6997522643[/flickr]\n\nWe have schemed and collaborated on 7 fun little projects together so far. Stayed tuned to my flickr account all week to see more of our artistic imaginings. My art direction, locations and story boards and Shanes light direction and mad skillz = stock images that break the mold a bit for stock images don''t you think?\n\nShane and I would like to thank his (Shane''s) cousin Ryan, for the use of this awesome ''67 Plymouth\n\n&nbsp;', 'artistic license', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1902-revision', '', '', '2012-03-19 13:19:29', '2012-03-19 19:19:29', '', 1902, 'http://tcd.spiraldesign.ca/1902-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
