(1990, 2, '2012-05-14 07:03:03', '2012-05-14 07:03:03', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nToday is the day! After months of hard work and anticipation, my new sites are launched! Designers, font aficionados, web geeks, and mid-century modern design lovers- I''m so excited for you to see them all.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTo start, I have a brand new logo (or should I say Coat of Arms!) for my the10centdesigner.com blog. I love it so much I''m having it screened onto my new skateboard this summer. Oh heck, I might even get my coat of arms tattooed over my foot it''s so fun and eye catching. The design has everything 10 cent- bold technicolor wings, wonder woman stars, fabulous girly shoes, and a fierce lion for protection. The blog has been constructed from scratch and perfectly meets my expectations and my style thanks to my wunderkind designer Asher Compton.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nI am also stoked to show you all my brand new photography site "LAP" . Vaunt Visual (Asher Compton) has designed something really fresh, very smart and super clean for this. I wanted to showcase my photography in a new and radical way and I think Vaunt Visual has created a photography site for me that does this masterfully.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOf course, I needed to rethink my interiors site as well "LAI". I love how the two sites relate yet retain their profession specific appeal.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nI asked my talented web designer Asher Compton to create something super new and shake up the internets with all of my new sites. I''m super stoked and excited to show you all what he created. I have asked Vaunt Visual to describe the entire process and the features of my new sites for you. Much Love to Vaunt Visual! thank you - 10cent\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTake it away Asher-\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Launching Like Rockets!!!', '', 'private', 'open', 'open', '', 'launching-like-rockets', '', '', '2012-05-15 14:20:39', '2012-05-15 14:20:39', '', 0, 'http://tcd.spiraldesign.ca/?p=1990', 0, 'post', '', 0),
